          "description": "It's the place to be for superb dental services. Dr. Jaron VanMeter is an excellent dentist. He's very caring and professional. He explains your treatment in detail. I had a crown done and I'm very happy with the results.\nMichele Becker the dental hygienist is very pleasant and skilled at her craft. She gives you good advice on preventative care. The staff is very accommodating and helpful.",
