          "description": "Amazing first visit! I recently had to change offices due to insurance and am so glad I did! The location is perfect, the building is nice and friendly, receptionist is great, and my hygienist and dentist were amazing. It\u2019s really important for me to find hygienist/dentist of color and they hit it out of the park with their staffing. I can often feel othered at NYC dentist, but felt right at home here. They were so soft and gentle, did more overall health exams than what I was use to. They also didn\u2019t try to upsell me on things, which was a problem previously. Often I\u2019d leave dentist feeling confused due to unexpected cost, but they were up front about everything. I will certainly be making this my home dentist as long as they will have me! Totally recommend.",
